Package com.groundupworks.wings.core

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlarmReceiver
    Receiver for alarms to trigger the WingsService.
    BootReceiver
    Receiver for system boot event schedule a trigger to the WingsService.
    Destination
    A destination that Wings can share to.
    RetryPolicy
    A class that calculates how far in the future to schedule the next attempt to share.
    ShareRequest
    A model object representing a share request.
    WingsDbHelper
    The Wings database helper that stores ShareRequest records and manages the state of those records.
    WingsInjector
    Injector for passing dependencies to Wings.
    WingsService
    An IntentService that processes ShareRequest.
